Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Papal visit, September 1987
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440ft1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Sep 1987
Papal visit crosses the entire continent to face all manner of religious problems from some 52 million US Catholics. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less